|GKBStandard Guilds:

|YKOStandard guilds are divided into 3 categories:
Melee, Caster, and Combo.  These categories are
based on their combat adjustments found in 
guildd.h.


|CKBMelee guilds (400+): |YKOBard, Cleric, Fighter, Garou,
Paladin, Priest.

|CKBCombo guilds (380-399): |YKONinja, Psionicist,
Swashbuckler, Thief.

|CKBCaster guilds (360-379): |YKOLunar, Mage

     |WKBMelee:   |RKB1:3 - 1:5
     |WKBCombo:   |RKB1:4 - 1:6
     |WKBCasters: |RKB1:5 - 1:7

|WKBNote: |YKOThe lower ratioed categories MAY
bump up the ratio if the spell warrants
the increase. eg: Bard wail also damages
the player while damaging the mob.

|CKBMythic Guilds: |RKB1:4 - 1:8







